Alleged murder fugitive Gerhard Jansen van Vuuren has been extradited from Brazil to South Africa. His plane touched down in the country a short while ago. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Alleged murder fugitive Gerhard Jansen van Vuuren has been extradited from Brazil to South Africa. His plane touched down in the country a short while ago. READ: SA murder-accused jailed in Brazil In 2011 he allegedly stabbed his ex-girlfriend, Andrea Venter. He attempted to commit suicide at the scene of the crime. While on bail, Van Vuuren fled the SA and was re-arrested in Brazil.